&lt;P&gt;The Governor of the North-West Region,&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P&gt;Considering the peaceful and hitch-free organisation of the September 30th, 2013 Municipal and Legislative Elections in our Region, conveys his deep appreciation to all the election stakeholders; Administrative Authorities, Forces of Law and Order, the electorate, as well as all Political, Religious, Traditional and Opinion leaders, every North-Westerner and friend of the North West for their contributions, peaceful participation as well as their wholehearted and dedicated efforts for the success of these elections.&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P&gt;He hereby calls on all to leave behind our differences and rally behind our newly elected leaders for a better North-West Region and a brighter future.&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P&gt;While urging you all to remain steadfast to Republican values and continue to exercise your civic rights and duties, he wishes you all and your families; A Happy and Prosperous New Year 2014. /-&lt;/P&gt;

&lt;P&gt;The North-West Region shall join the International Community to celebrate the World Philosophy Day the 21st November 2013 in GBHS Bali, MEZAM Division.&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P&gt;This is a day set aside by UNESCO to give the discipline(Philosophy), the importance it deserves.&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P&gt;This year\'s celebrations have been placed under the theme : \&quot;Philosophy and History\&quot;.&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P&gt;During the Celebrations, students will carry out activities like sketches, recitation of poems, song, etc., related to the theme of the year.&lt;/P&gt;

&lt;P&gt;Il m\'est revenu que de faux documents(reçus de dépôts de dossiers) seraient en circulation entre les mains des usagers(notamment les reçus de dépôts de dossiers de Carte Grise et d\'autres documents de transports). Les documents incriminés sont supposés avoir été établis par des personnels de la Délégation Régionale des Transports.&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P&gt;Par conséquent, il est porté à l\'attention du grand public que de tels documents sont illégaux et par conséquent, toute personne surprise en possession de tels document sera mise aux arrêts pour justification de la provenance de ceux-ci.&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P&gt;Par ailleurs, tout personnel appartenant à mes services qui sera reconnu de la délivrance de tels documents sera sanctionné conformément à la réglémentation en vigueur.&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P&gt;Les Officiers de Police Judiciaire en charge de la tenue de la campagne de sécurité routière sont chargé en ce qui les concerne de l\'implémentation du contenu de cette note de service.&lt;/P&gt;

&lt;P&gt;My attention has been drawn to the fact that fake and fraudulent deposit receipts(depots) have been discovered in circulation in the hands of users(&lt;STRONG&gt;notably receipts for deposition of&lt;/STRONG&gt; &lt;STRONG&gt;Carte Grise and other Transport documents&lt;/STRONG&gt;). These fraudulent documents are said to have been issued by some officials of the Regional Delegation of Transport.&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P&gt;The general public is by this means informed that all such documents are illegal. Therefore, anyone found in position of such documents may be arrested to justify the obtaining of such documents.&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P&gt;Moreover, any official of the Delegation of Transport found to be associated with the issuance of such documents shall be sanctioned in accordance with the existing regulation.&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P&gt;The O.P.J on Road Safety campaign are charged with the responsibility of the implementation of the content of this notice&lt;/P&gt;

&lt;P&gt;Le Gouverneur de la Région du Nord-Ouest porte à la connaissance du grand public que des campagnes de locales de vaccinations gratuites contre la poliomyélite seront organisées dans la Région et s'adresseront aux enfants de 0 à 5 ans.&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P&gt;Pour ce faire, des équipes mobiles feront des descentes sur le terrain pour l'administration des dits vaccins en porte-à-porte pendant que ces vaccinations se tiendront aussi dans tous les centres de santé de la Région.&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P&gt;Il est à noter que ces campagnes,&amp;nbsp;fruits du partenariat entre le Gouvernement camerounais &amp;nbsp;et les organismes GAVI, OMS, UNICEF etc..., se feront en deux phases : &lt;/P&gt;
&lt;UL&gt;
&lt;LI&gt;du 22 au 24 novembre 2013; 
&lt;LI&gt;du 20 au 22 décembre 2013.&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;/UL&gt;

&lt;P&gt;The Governor of the North-West Region hereby would like to inform the general public that some local vaccination campaigns against the Poliomyelitis shall be organize within the entire region to the attention of 0-5 years old childs.&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P&gt;Therefore, some mobile units will move round for door-to-door to administer the vaccine but vaccination will also be going on in all health units.&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P&gt;The vaccination is completely&amp;nbsp;free of charges because the Cameroon Government and its partners GAVI, WHO, UNICEF etc have already pay for it. and shall take place in two phases :&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;UL&gt;
&lt;LI&gt;from&amp;nbsp;22nd to 24th November 2013; 
&lt;LI&gt;from&amp;nbsp;20th&amp;nbsp;to 22nd December 2013.&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;/UL&gt;

&lt;P&gt;In view of activities marking the celebrations of the 22nd edition of the International Day of Person Living with Disabilities on the 3rd of December 2013, based on the theme &quot;&lt;STRONG&gt;&lt;EM&gt;Break barriers, open doors: for an inclusive society for all&lt;/EM&gt;&lt;/STRONG&gt;&quot;, we are pleased to invite you to partner with us.&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P&gt;About 15% to 20% of people in every community have some level of impairment. Commonly these persons are excluded from development efforts&amp;nbsp; where are such efforts, will be incomplete without them. Service providers and the North West Regional Delegation of Social Affairs are adopting a sustainable approach by empowering 2(two) Associations of Persons with Disabilities to start or scale up income generating activities.&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P&gt;We need a budget of 1 115 000&amp;nbsp;CFA to carry out this activity and others as outlined below:&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;UL&gt;
&lt;LI&gt;Information and Sensitization on the theme; 
&lt;LI&gt;Empowerment of two associations; 
&lt;LI&gt;Award of prizes for socio-cultural activities; 
&lt;LI&gt;Sport; 
&lt;LI&gt;Talent exhibition etc.&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;/UL&gt;
&lt;P&gt;We therefore are calling on the good will of all to adhere to a partnership with the Organization Committee headed by the Governor of the North West Region by funding one or more of these activities.&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P&gt;Thanks in advance for your interest in supporting persons living with disabilities.&lt;/P&gt;
